TopicTitle: Where can I get some wheels like these?

Articles.Content: I saw this rover and wanted to know if anyone knew that mod they were part of.

There was an old mod:

http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/47765-Space-Factory

But I have no idea whether it works in 0.90. Probably it would require to update its cfg manually.

Basically, such parts/ships are "Lunokhod" or "Luna-17"
They are not in stock, so moved to add-on affairs.
